"title": "5881: immaturity",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5881: immaturity",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The result of insufficient growth, or a failure to develop to one's full potential.</p>\n<h2>Marks of physical immaturity</h2>\n<h3>Pride</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:1-2Sam15:4\">2SA 15:1–15:4</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of wise counsel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18\">DEU 21:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:8\">1KI 12:8</a></p>\n<h3>Tactlessness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:13-1Kgs12:14\">1KI 12:13–12:14</a></p>\n<h3>Lack of respect</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:23\">2KI 2:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:18\">JOB 19:18</a></p>\n<h3>Weakness of character</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:7\">2CH 13:7</a></p>\n<h3>Foolishness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:15\">PRO 22:15</a></p>\n<h3>Lack of understanding</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:39\">DEU 1:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:4\">PRO 1:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:11\">JON 4:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:11\">1CO 13:11</a></p>\n<h3>Lack of self-control</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:6\">TIT 2:6</a></p>\n<h3>Disgrace</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:15\">PRO 29:15</a></p>\n<h3>Waste</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:13\">LUK 15:13</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual immaturity is to be avoided</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:20\">1CO 14:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1\">HEB 6:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:9\">2CO 13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a> <em>The word “perfection” may be understood in terms of maturity</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13\">EPH 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">EPH 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28\">COL 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">COL 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:4\">JAS 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h2>Marks of spiritual immaturity</h2>\n<h3>Backsliding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:20-Matt13:21\">MAT 13:20–13:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:16-Mark4:17\">MRK 4:16–4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:13\">LUK 8:13</a> <em>Jesus Christ to his disciples.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:8-Gal4:9\">GAL 4:8–4:9</a></p>\n<h3>An over-sensitive conscience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:2\">ROM 14:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Lack of spiritual understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:1-1Cor3:2\">1CO 3:1–3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:16-Matt11:19\">MAT 11:16–11:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:31-Luke7:35\">LUK 7:31–7:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:11-Heb5:14\">HEB 5:11–5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Divisiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:3\">1CO 3:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Instability</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:6-Jas1:7\">JAS 1:6–1:7</a></p>\n<h3>Pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:6\">1TI 3:6</a></strong> <em>The church overseer must be a spiritually mature person.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>Remedies for immaturity</h2>\n<h3>Confession of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:13\">PRO 28:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:13-Jer3:22\">JER 3:13–3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Discipline</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:11-Prov3:12\">PRO 3:11–3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:67-Ps119:71\">PSA 119:67–119:71</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1-1Pet4:2\">1PE 4:1–4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:19\">REV 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer and meditation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:97-Ps119:99\">PSA 119:97–119:99</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:27\">PSA 119:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:17-John17:19\">JHN 17:17–17:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26\">ROM 8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:16\">HEB 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:25\">JAS 1:25</a></p>",
